headline: Is Starbucks’ AI Push Proof We’re in an AI Bubble?
summary: Artificial intelligence (AI) is reshaping industries at an unprecedented pace, automating routine tasks, analyzing vast datasets, and enabling new forms of creativity that were once unimaginable. In workplaces, AI tools like chatbots and predictive analytics are streamlining workflows, allowing employees to focus on higher-value activities.
